body:
Ok, cool. We introduced a new version of some of the linting tools, so I tweaked and fixed that. I rolled back the upgrade to redux-form, since it is going to be a bigger task. I think this is ready to go.

Also, is this something we want to do long term? Greenkeeper will file PRs for new libraries, and hopefully a good enough test suite will make this very easy to keep up to date.

@rehandalal r?

